OL,4,CRetailers call for 'Shop Out to Help
OL,5,COut' scheme when stores reopen
OL,6, A group of big names in fashion and
OL,7, retail are campaigning for the
OL,8, government to provide more support for
OL,9, small independent shops.
OL,11,FThey want the chancellor to offer a
OL,12,F"Shop Out to Help Out" scheme to get
OL,13,Fconsumers spending again when
OL,14,Fnon-essential shops reopen on 12 April.
OL,16,FIt would cover 50% of a shopper's
OL,17,Fcosts, up to #10, on Monday to
OL,18,FWednesdays for a month.
OL,20,FAnd it would only apply at physical
OL,21,Fstores with fewer than 10 staff.
